These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, begonia, iris, daffodil
House: farmhouse, cottage, ranch-style, victorian
1. the farmhouse house is somewhere to the left of the ranch-style house##5
2. the person who growsbegonia is not the farmhouse house##6
3. the farmhouse house is on the right of the victorian house##1
4. the person who growsiris is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
5. the person who growslily is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
6. the farmhouse house is not the person who growsiris##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | begonia   | daffodil    | lily    | iris |
| Sport      | victorian | farmhouse | ranch-style | cottage |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, dahlia, aconite, lily
House: craftsman, palace, townhouse, ranch-style
1. the craftsman house is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsdahlia is somewhere to the left of the person who growsaconite##5
3. the ranch-style house is somewhere to the left of the person who growslily##5
4. the person who growsdahlia is not the palace house##6
5. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
6. the craftsman house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
7. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
8. the person who growsaconite is somewhere to the left of the person who growstulip##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | dahlia  | aconite    | tulip | lily    |
| Food       | ranch-style | palace | townhouse  | craftsman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
4 different games are played: domino, scrabble, backgammon, mah-jongg
City: hannover, paris, boston, edinburgh
1. the person playing mah-jongg is not the person traveling to hannover##6
2. the person traveling to paris is not the person playing backgammon##6
3. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
4. the person traveling to paris is the person playing domino##1
5. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
6. the person playing domino is in an odd position##4
7. the person traveling to hannover is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person traveling to boston is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | mah-jongg       | scrabble  | domino  | backgammon |
| Job        | boston | edinburgh | paris | hannover  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, potato, pear, pineapple
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, may, january, december
1. the person eating pear is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
2. the person eating potato is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5
3. the person who's birthday is in december is not the person eating potato##6
4. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##5
5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
6. the person eating pineapple is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | potato | pear | pineapple     | artichoke |
| Transport   | may     | january    | june | december    |

