.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, soul, metal, techno
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, november, september, may
1. the fan hip-hop is on the left of the fan techno##1
2. the fan techno is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##5
3. the fan techno is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5
4. the fan soul is not the person who's birthday is in may##6
5. the person who's birthday is in october is not the fan hip-hop##6
6. the fan metal is on the left of the fan soul##1
7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | hip-hop        | techno | metal | soul |
| Transport   | may | october | november     | september   |

