.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
4 different games are played: bridge, monopoly, whist, poker
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, montecristo, pall-mall, fonseca
1. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
2. the person playing poker is not the montecristo-smoker##6
3. the old-henry-smoker is on the far right##1
4. the montecristo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the fonseca-smoker##5
5. the person playing whist is the person playing whist##1
6. the person playing whist is somewhere to the left of the old-henry-smoker##5
7. the person playing whist is somewhere to the left of the person playing bridge##5
8. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the left of the fonseca-smoker##5
9. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the left of the fonseca-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | monopoly | whist    | bridge  | poker   |
| Nationality   | pall-mall  | fonseca | montecristo | old-henry |

