.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, almond-milk, tea, fanta
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, rose, balloon-flower, azalea
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is not the person drinking almond-milk##6
3. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who growsrose##1
4. the person who growstulip is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
5. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far left##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who growstulip##1
7. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person who growstulip##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | fanta | almond-milk     | tea | iced-tea |
| Music-Genre   | balloon-flower | tulip | azalea      | rose         |

