.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, magic-tricks, drawing, woodworking
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, cain, bolivar, blend
1. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
2. the blend-smoker is somewhere to the left of the bolivar-smoker##5
3. the blend-smoker is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
4. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the cain-smoker##3
6. the dannemann-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
8. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not the blend-smoker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | magic-tricks  | baking        | drawing      | woodworking          |
| Job        | dannemann | cain | blend | bolivar |

