.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-9::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, time-travel, epic, satire
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, tulip, iris, bellflower
1. the person watching crime movies is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growstulip is not the person watching satire movies##6
3. the person who growsazalea is somewhere to the right of the person watching epic movies##5
4. the person who growsbellflower is in an even position##4
5. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
6. the person who growsbellflower is the person watching epic movies##1
7. the person watching crime movies is not the person who growsbellflower##6
8. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching satire movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | crime  | epic | satire    | time-travel |
| Transport   | tulip | bellflower | iris | azalea  |

