.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, lemonade, iced-tea
There are 4 different nationalities: american, nigerian, german, french
1. the american is not the person drinking cola##6
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
3. the french is the french##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the french##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is not the french##6
6. the nigerian is not the person drinking sprite##6
7. the french is in an even position##4
8. the person drinking lemonade is the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | lemonade | cola        | iced-tea  | sprite     |
| Sport   | american     | french | nigerian | german |

