.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, orange, black, pink
City: boston, rome, prague, venice
1. the person who likes blue is on the left or right of the person who likes pink##3
2. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the left of the person who likes blue##5
3. the person traveling to prague is not the person who likes black##6
4. the person who likes orange is between the person traveling to venice and the person who likes black##2
5. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
6. the person traveling to rome is between the person traveling to boston and the person who likes blue##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | black | orange    | blue | pink |
| Music-Genre   | boston         | rome | venice   | prague     |

