There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, spanish, german, australian
1. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the right of the german##5
2. the person who's birthday is in february is not the malaysian##6
3. the spanish is the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the spanish is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
5. the german is not the person who's birthday is in february##6
6. the person who's birthday is in july is not the malaysian##6
7. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##5
8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | october  | september | july | february |
| Transport   | german | malaysian     | australian     | spanish    |

